{"id":600134,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/【异闻观止】中国模特罢演dg秀共演-not-me行动/","date":"2018-11-21T20:01:07Z","modified":"2018-11-22T18:55:57Z","title":"【异闻观止】中国模特罢演DG秀共演 NOT ME行动","content":"<p>编者按：据网络消息，意大利奢侈品牌杜嘉班纳广告引起“辱华风波”继续发酵，@章子怡 、@陈坤 、@Dear-迪丽热巴 等明星表示不出席DG秀。有媒体连线模特公司@东方宾利 了解罢演始末：模特们表示本想等品牌方发布道歉声明，但没有等来，最终全部撤回，不考虑经济损失，完全出于爱国考虑。参加此次活动的中国模特共计300余人。根据不完全统计，<a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E9%99%88%E5%86%B0%E5%BD%AC%E5%BD%AC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@陈冰彬彬</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E9%87%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%B7%9D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@金大川</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E7%BA%AA%E5%87%8C%E5%B0%98chan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@纪凌尘chan</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E8%96%9B%E5%86%AC%E7%90%AA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@薛冬琪</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/Zhang-%E6%96%87%E8%BE%89\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@Zhang-文辉</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E5%B7%A9%E5%9B%BD%E8%B1%AAgong\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@巩国豪gong</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E5%88%98%E6%98%A5%E6%9D%B0%E5%91%80\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@刘春杰呀</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E5%80%AA%E6%B5%A9%E7%84%B6nihao\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@倪浩然nihao</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E7%8E%8B%E6%B6%B5Whan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@王涵Whan</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E5%88%98%E6%AC%A2Huannn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@刘欢Huannn</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E8%B5%B5%E4%BF%8A%E8%8E%89-\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@赵俊莉-</a> <a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E6%9E%97%E6%B9%98%E6%B9%98_\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@林湘湘_</a> 张新成、周雅亭、李霖梓、董翰宬、陈圣、梁继远等众多中国模特已经退出<em class=\"s-color-red\">DG</em>上海<em class=\"s-color-red\">秀</em>，并在社交媒体发起“Not Me”行动。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-600148\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/9-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"236\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chines